  • File Manager

    Just like on your computer, you can manage your files quickly and easily with the help of:

    right-click context menus - for quick access to various file manipulation options;

    drag-and-drop - for uploading new files/folders from your device in an instant;

    quick shortcut keys - for searching through the file/folder listings of a specific directory via Ctrl+F; for copying/moving files between directories via Ctrl+C/Ctrl+X and Ctrl+V (you can also use them for moving files between different windows and from your PC to the File Manager).

File Manager

Just like on your computer, you can manage your files quickly and easily with the help of:

right-click context menus - for quick access to various file manipulation options;

drag-and-drop - for uploading new files/folders from your device in an instant;

quick shortcut keys - for searching through the file/folder listings of a specific directory via Ctrl+F; for copying/moving files between directories via Ctrl+C/Ctrl+X and Ctrl+V (you can also use them for moving files between different windows and from your PC to the File Manager).
